Paysafe Group PLC, formerly known as Optimal Payments PLC and Neovia Financial PLC, is an online payments company based in the Isle of Man and regulated in the United Kingdom. It is the provider of the NETBANX gateway, Neteller e-money payments and free person-to-person money transfer service, and the Net+ prepaid card products used by merchants and consumers in over 200 countries. Paysafe is authorised by the Financial Conduct Authority. The company is listed on the London Stock Exchange and it is a constituent of the FTSE 250 Index.
